  "name": "Way of Onmitu Speed Cloness",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Fon.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a part of the requirements of this jutsu, you must know the <em><strong>Way of Onmitsu: Shunpo</strong></em> Jutsu. Utilizing Shunpo, you move so quickly throughout the area that you create a number of fleeting clones of yourself equal to twice your Proficiency Bonus that are completely indistinguishable from your real self, even with true sight. They each perfectly mimic your movements and speech, and must each occupy their own individual spaces within the range of this jutsu.</p><p>Until the start of your next turn, you are treated as being Invisible to any creature that can see or sense you whose passive Perception is equal to or lower than half of your base movement speed rounded down to the nearest five feet.</p><p>If their passive Perception would be lower than this value by 5 or more, your attacks against them gain a +1 bonus to their critical threat range for the duration of this jutsu.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost by 3, and the radius by 5 feet.</p>",
